{"tid":1822191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港獨立是唯一出路","createTime":"2020-01-12T19:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T22:16:05.000Z","uid":337052,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"802f1dedd071a8a8c349598d72fa5c1629a5c450","tid":1822191,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T19:20:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港獨立是唯一出路</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n沒有主權沒有民主<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo/?fbid=10156368922551065&amp;set=a.10151242056081065\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto%2F%3Ffbid%3D10156368922551065%26set%3Da.10151242056081065&d=EP%2BJfZZVzGvO4DQPpGaiyPilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=a88a1dab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo/?fbid=10156368922551065&amp;set=a.10151242056081065</a>"},{"pid":"35140afef2cf1e7c60103c1637541f951cbaf0a7","tid":1822191,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T19:38:30.000Z","msg":"這次，台灣人民勇敢而自信的決定，讓世界看見台灣人民的聲音。<br />\n  <br />\n過去這半年來，有許多香港的年輕朋友，在台灣各個角落自發的舉著牌子和旗子，告訴台灣人民香港所發生的事情。<br />\n  <br />\n在網路上，台灣的年輕人也透過社群和香港同步感受民主自由的重要。<br />\n  <br />\n選前一天我說，全世界都會看到，台灣人守住了這座民主堡壘。<br />\n  <br />\n香港的朋友，你們看到了嗎？"},{"pid":"99f3935572b11cf1555d399566c126e480ef0e0c","tid":1822191,"uid":233156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T21:06:38.000Z","msg":"認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eab30c43d7764ee49e5abaa157cb40e9147a6eee","tid":1822191,"uid":216008,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T21:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CtTpjx6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCtTpjx6.jpg&h=1d68ecee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"439f92bb11922c8a6e063adb3cd37df69264985a","tid":1822191,"uid":82155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T21:12:37.000Z"